<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/general.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/join.css">
        <title>Malaysian Club of Chicago - Join Us</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        {{>navbar}}
        <div id="right">
            <div style="min-height: 120px;" class="vert-block">
                <div style="padding: 30px 0; font-size: 19px; max-width: 70%" class="text">
                    <h1 style="line-height: 1.2em; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;">Malaysian Club of Chicago Membership Form</h1>
                    <p>Being an MCC member will give you and your family a discount on admission for many of MCC upcoming events. Becoming a MCC member is FREE! So please take this opportunity to fill out and submit the form. We are looking forward to seeing you at our future events.</p>
                    <form id="join">
                        <div id="inputs">
                            <label for="name" style="margin-right: 2.8em;">Your Name:</label>
                            <input id="name" placeholder="Full Name"><br>
                            <label for="email" style="margin-right: 3em;">Your Email:</label>
                            <input id="email" placeholder="Email Address"><br>
                            <label for="hometown" style="margin-right: 0.5em;">Your Hometown:</label>
                            <input id="hometown" placeholder="Hometown in Malaysia"><br>
                        </div>
                        <label for="aff">Malaysian Affiliation:</label><br>
                        <textarea id="aff" name="aff" rows="5" cols="40" placeholder="Type about your affiliation with the Malaysian culture."></textarea><br>
                        <input id="submit" type="submit">
                    </form>
                    <div style="display: none; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; height: 300px;" id="process">
                        <h3 id="res">Sending your form... Please do not close this window.</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <script src="./js/join.js"></script>
            <div style="display: block; height: 4vh;"></div>
            {{>footer}}
        </div>
    </body>
</html>